name: ExportOptionsTIFF

properties.name: imageColorSpace
properties.description: The color space of the exported file.

properties.name: resolution
properties.description: The resolution of the exported file.

properties.name: antiAliasing
properties.description: Should the resulting image be antialiased.

properties.name: lZWCompression
properties.description: Compress TIFF file with LZW Compression when exporting.

properties.name: byteOrder
properties.description: Mac or PC byte order when exporting.

properties.name: embedICCProfile
properties.description: Embed an ICC profile when exporting.

properties.name: saveMultipleArtboards
properties.description: All the artboards or range of the artboards will be exported.

properties.name: artboardRange
properties.description: If SaveMultipleArtboards is true,this will be considered for multi-asset extraction which specifies artboard range.Empty string will extracts all the artboards.Default is empty string.

description: Options which may be supplied when exporting a document as a TIFF file.
